---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Speaking - Javi Rubio">
  <div class="speaking-container">
    <h1>Speaking</h1>

    <p class="intro">I regularly speak at corporate events and tech conferences:</p>

    <ul class="talks-list">
      <li class="talk">
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IHIsuIlSiio" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <strong>Documenting APIs</strong>
        </a>
        <span class="separator">·</span>
        <span class="event">Software Crafters Barcelona, 2025</span>
      </li>

      <li class="talk">
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HsPIX0tNlO8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <strong>AI in support teams</strong>
        </a>
        <span class="separator">·</span>
        <span class="event">Software Crafters Barcelona, 2024</span>
      </li>

      <li class="talk">
        <strong>Enterprise knowledge management</strong>
        <span class="separator">·</span>
        <span class="event">CAS (Agile Spain Conference), Madrid, 2024</span>
      </li>

      <li class="talk">
        <strong>We're capitalists</strong>
        <span class="separator">·</span>
        <span class="event">Software Crafters Barcelona, 2023</span>
      </li>

      <li class="talk">
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SYnLZCFtims" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <strong>#NoMeetings: How to have fewer, more efficient meetings</strong>
        </a>
        <span class="separator">·</span>
        <span class="event">CAS, Santiago de Compostela, 2022</span>
      </li>

      <li class="talk">
        <strong>Great interactions generate great products</strong>
        <span class="separator">·</span>
        <span class="event">CAS, Vitoria, 2018 (workshop)</span>
      </li>

      <li class="talk">
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1fs9DPdTKS8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <strong>DevOps: From the trenches to the boardroom</strong>
        </a>
        <span class="separator">·</span>
        <span class="event">CAS, Alicante, 2016</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .speaking-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .talks-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .talk {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .talk::before {
    content: "–";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-gray-medium);
  }

  .talk strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .separator {
    margin: 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-medium);
  }

  .event {
    color: var(--color-gray-medium);
  }

  .talk a {
    color: var(--color-turquoise);
  }

  .talk a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .talk {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
